Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.41,0:01:52.92,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}光芒照射的另一端
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.22,0:01:55.90,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}用手遮起来看过去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:01:58.17,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}从指间缝隙里看到的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:01.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}是那天立下誓约的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.72,0:02:04.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}超越音速
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.55,0:02:07.24,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}切开暴风
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.67,0:02:09.54,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}用魔法的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.57,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}来守护你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.96,0:02:15.36,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}即使在痛苦想要哭泣的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.79,0:02:18.20,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}我也在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.62,0:02:21.13,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}那片湛蓝湛蓝的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.48,0:02:25.24,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}绝不让给任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:28.46,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}来  一起飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:33.66,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}将喷薄而出的勇气化作盾牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.47,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}展翅高飞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.52,0:02:38.82,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}把袭来的黑暗全都
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:40.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}一扫而光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:44.93,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}要变得
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.11,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}比昨天的我更强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:55.29,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}现在  就向着那闪耀的天空而去
